dbt2-extensions (0.61.7-1PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial package for the DBT-2 PostgreSQL C stored functions.
  * Build version-specific packages for PostgreSQL 14 through 18.
  * Keep upstream SQL extension version 0.45.0 distinct from kit version.
  * Honor pg_buildext's PG_CONFIG for correct per-version ABI builds.
  * Preserve reproducible paths in LLVM bitcode and generate shlib dependencies.
  * Verify source integrity and generate automatic debug symbols.

